All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Attribute
Represents a general or subcategory-specific Attribute.
Category
Represents the broad category that the item belongs to.
GeneralAttributes
A set of Attributes that applies to all items.
GeneralItemAttributes
A special set of attributes that generally apply to all/most items.
Index  
Item
Represents an "Item" or "Listing" as it is represented in the app.
ItemAttribute
Represents an Attribute of an Item.
ItemMeasurement
Represents a measurement of an item.
ItemSize
Represents the size of an item.
Measurement
Represents a measurement that should be taken of an item in a given subcategory.
Methods  
Recommendation
Represents a recommended value for an Attribute or other value like Size.
Size
Represents a Size option.
Subcategory
Represents the Subcategory of the Item.
Template
Represents a set of fields to be completed by the user.
